     * Lisp in JSON
     * version, code, data
     * Expr -> ["op", <args...>]
     * Str, Num, Bool, Null -> themselves
     * List -> [[...]]
     * Hash -> [{...}]

     * TestML Types
       * regex, func, none, error, native

     * Cooked vs Raw values

